snippet.title: GTFO | Rundown 005 / REBIRTH - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Major update Rebirth is AVAILABLE NOW for everyone that owns GTFO!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/493520/GTFO/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=yt-discovery&utm_campaign=awo&utm_content=cta

GTFO is a terrifying 4 player co-op game for hardcore FPS players, brought to you by the game designer behind PAYDAY 1 & 2. Players get to play as a team of scavengers, forced to explore and extract valuable artefacts from a vast underground complex that has been overrun by horrifying monsters. Gather weapons, tools, and resources to help you survive - and work to unearth the answers about your past and how to escape.

Join the official GTFO Discord at: https://discord.gg/gtfo
Become an Ambassador at: http://www.gtfothegame.com
Follow the game on Twitter @ https://twitter.com/tenchambers

About 10 Chambers:
Founded in 2015, 10 Chambers is a game studio based in Stockholm, Sweden. The studio was founded by Ulf Andersson who also founded Overkill Software and is the game designer behind PAYDAY 1 & 2. GTFO is the debut title from the studio. More information about 10 Chambers is available at www.10chambers.com. For press and media enquires, contact robin@10chambers.com.

#GTFOtheGame #GTFO #10Chambers
